    "english": "During a <disastrous> storm, the young <orphan> Emily sought refuge in an <outdated> shelter.",
    "chinese": "在一场<灾难性的>风暴中，年轻的<孤儿>艾米丽在一个<过时的>避难所中寻求庇护。"
